      <h2 class="section__heading">Payroll subscription &amp; tax-table errors.</h2>
      <p class="section__lede">PS-series errors are payroll-specific and usually involve the payroll service subscription, the tax-table download, or paycheck-processing validation. Often resolvable by verifying subscription status before assuming a deeper problem.</p>
